Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.43,0:00:18.40,Lucy-Song-Title,,0,0,0,,[I want to be a rainbow]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:29.86,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa hoshifuru yoru ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.11,0:00:36.79,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono tomoshibi wo keshi wa shinai to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:47.92,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa akane no asa ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.17,0:00:56.85,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wakaba ni somaru haru wo yobou to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.13,0:01:08.74,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Ono utsu hibiki michi hiraku utagoe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:20.63,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kodama ga mune ni hazunde kuru no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.91,0:01:26.47,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono oosora no niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.75,0:01:36.27,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kibou ni todoku niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:29.86,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow I made on that starry night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.11,0:00:36.79,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To not let this flame die
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:47.92,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow made on that brilliant red morning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.17,0:00:56.85,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To call out for spring, dyed with young leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.13,0:01:08.74,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Cutting axes open up roads, under the sound of singing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:20.63,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,The echoes bounce around in my chest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.91,0:01:26.47,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow in this big sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.75,0:01:36.27,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow that reaches out to hope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.35,0:01:47.19,Lucy-Ep-Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,306.667)\fade(100,110)}Ep. 36 - Five Shillings in the Nest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.26,0:01:51.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.69,0:01:53.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Take it easy, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:54.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of your faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:55.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.09,0:02:01.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When Lucy and I went to fetch Doctor Deighton,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.21,0:02:04.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,we were awfully surprised\Nto see our old cabin in flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.59,0:02:14.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The one who ordered them\Nto set fire to our old cabin was Mr. Pettywell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.58,0:02:20.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My, my, if it isn't Mr. Popple's daughters?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.58,0:02:22.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You came all the way here to see the show?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:28.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Silver, if he looks at you the wrong way,\Nfeel free to bite him to death, if needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.39,0:02:34.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy, aren't you going to stop Little?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:41.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, at that moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.10,0:02:45.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I even thought it'd be better\Nif Little tore Mr. Pettywell's bulldog to shreds.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.58,0:02:55.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.20,0:02:58.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.69,0:03:09.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Little, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.60,0:03:13.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What? Really gonna stop now?\NWouldn't it be better to let them do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.20,0:03:14.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:16.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It see, that's very clever of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:19.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There's no dog that's be on par with Silver\Nin the entirety of Adelaide.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:22.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little wouldn't lose to that bulldog!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.52,0:03:25.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, why won't we let them do it to know for sure?\NOughta be interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.75,0:03:27.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:31.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Pettywell, a man such as you\Nis indeed the worst calamity that can befall one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.41,0:03:35.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Doctor Deighton, do me a favor\Nand leave that house soon, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:38.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're living on my land now, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.02,0:03:41.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I said it before, I'll say it now:\NI'm not going anywhere! Period.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.47,0:03:46.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd that'd be bothersome. Then, how should I\Ndo away with that house - burn it or tear it down?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.38,0:03:47.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I said I'm not going...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.71,0:03:49.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, I'll wait for just a month more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:54.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In one month from now, I'll put into action\Nwhat I just said, without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.72,0:03:55.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.99,0:04:00.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, I wonder if Mr. Pettywell\Nis actually gonna drive you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:01.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm sure he will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.74,0:04:05.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,After all, his plan is to fill that plot\Nwith houses and sell them all separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.54,0:04:07.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, where will you go, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:08.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I've nowhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.52,0:04:13.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If they tear that house down, I'll just stretch a tent\Nlike in the old times and keep practicing from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:16.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,They'll tear the tent down in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:19.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, I think it's best that you\Nstart looking for where to go next, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:22.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No! Whatever happens,\NI won't yield an inch there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:23.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I won't yield!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:39.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:41.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.33,0:04:43.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Just a bit more, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:47.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If only there was something we could ride,\Nwe'd make it to your place fast and with comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.69,0:04:49.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But around here, there's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:50.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Look, look, look, a carriage like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:54.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:04:57.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, don't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:04:59.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:02.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh... Right, I'll keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:05.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta do my best for a little longer,\Nuntil we get to Angas Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:09.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up, Doctor!\NDon't give up, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.84,0:05:12.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Almost there, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:05:13.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:13.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:15.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:21.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh... Doctor Deighton has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:22.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What about Kate and Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.19,0:05:23.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Coming with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.79,0:05:28.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,G'day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.67,0:05:30.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Quite a misfortune you've been through, Mr. Popple?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:32.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Just injured my leg a bit due to a misstep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.91,0:05:35.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I owe you one for taking all the trouble to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:36.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, I'm a doctor, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.82,0:05:38.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how far the patient is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:40.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Don't move, don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.99,0:05:42.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So, which of the legs?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:43.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The right one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.33,0:05:44.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? This one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:46.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, let's see, let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:48.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that looks awfully swollen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:49.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, and with a bit of throbbing pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.90,0:05:52.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this doesn't look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:55.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If I move it like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:57.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:06:00.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That cabin was on fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:04.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Pettywell wants to build\Na new house there and sell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.11,0:06:08.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Your father and Ben, as well as Mr. Jamling\Nall worked hard to expand that tiny cabin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:12.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's no longer our house,\NI wouldn't want to see it go up in flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:14.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That'd probably sadden your father too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:20.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:23.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, yes, yes. And if I do this, how is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:24.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:26.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hurts the most this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.62,0:06:27.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.93,0:06:31.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, seems you've a fracture in your bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:35.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That was an awfully inopportune\Nmisstep on my part.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.30,0:06:38.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Still, it's a fate vastly preferable\Nto being crushed under the rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:41.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This kind of injury can heal perfectly\Nin just a month or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:43.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A month?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:46.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, are you saying\Nit'll take one month to heal?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.14,0:06:47.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:50.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But then, I won't be able to work\Nfor a whole month, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:53.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you exert yourself,\Nthe fracture will only expand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.40,0:06:56.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,One month, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.15,0:07:00.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,According to Mr. Pettywell,\NI also have only a month to leave my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:01.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's just outrageous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.03,0:07:04.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You built that house with your own hands, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.91,0:07:07.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And I also came to like it quite a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:11.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,By a stroke of ill fortune,\Nthat land fell into Mr. Pettywell's hands, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.92,0:07:13.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve always been an unlucky fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:16.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But then... Do you have any other place to go to?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:18.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,For the time being...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:21.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'd rather say it's best that you\Nrefrain from thinking about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:24.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, would you come to stay with us again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:26.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.49,0:07:29.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I've already delivered\Na great deal of nuisance to your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:30.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.85,0:07:34.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind it. When it comes to dwelling,\NI'll find some, sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.29,0:07:36.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That reminds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.63,0:07:40.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I could try working\Nat a new city hospital that opens soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:44.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, I said! No! Don't move, Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.09,0:07:47.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This one is an awfully good soap.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:49.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it smell good?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:52.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Look, the foam is coming out nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:54.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! No! You gotta stand still!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.73,0:07:56.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Stand still, you! Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:08:02.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh. Tell me, why are you\Nthat opposed to being clean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.70,0:08:06.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy, you’re the one\Nwho detests bathing the most here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:08.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little is just taking after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:13.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, I love taking baths now, is that clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.71,0:08:15.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't move, Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.70,0:08:20.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! No! Didn’t I tell you to stand still?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:21.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:25.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Oh no! Wait! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.60,0:08:29.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:31.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:35.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:44.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.76,0:08:47.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.28,0:08:50.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.12,0:08:51.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You’re not getting away with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:56.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:57.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.44,0:09:03.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:05.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, isn't it Little?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:07.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What’s with that fancy dress of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:10.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! No! Little...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.25,0:09:11.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:19.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:24.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you find that stuff tasty, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:26.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A kid won’t be able to understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:30.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... John, would you like a shot too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.62,0:09:32.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I’m good, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:36.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,John is a grown-up too,\Nbut he detests the booze.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.81,0:09:39.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't drink, you can’t become a grown-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:44.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But John is engaged to Clara already.\NDoesn’t that make him a grown-up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.40,0:09:47.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.29,0:09:49.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When are you two getting married?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:53.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well... Someday, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.89,0:09:56.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, please pour a bit for me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:09:58.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? You wanna drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.29,0:10:03.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good, good, good. Yes, but no need\Nto say “a bit.” Have plenty, plenty. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.22,0:10:04.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:10.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, John, you drink alcohol too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.87,0:10:13.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I was surprised a great deal too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:14.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.74,0:10:16.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right... Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:25.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't force yourself to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:27.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:29.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll drink it normally now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:31.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.64,0:10:32.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:34.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:36.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Splendid, splendid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.01,0:10:38.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Seems foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.09,0:10:42.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's get to eating now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:46.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What was that ruckus about just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.77,0:10:48.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,John was drinking alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:50.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That’s all?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:54.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's been about a year since I last\Nhad a meal together with the Popples.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:58.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Doctor, come sit down here, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.90,0:11:01.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate, call your father here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.17,0:11:02.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:06.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true a while month should pass\Nbefore father’s leg can fully heal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:07.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:12.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, mother, he wouldn’t be able\Nto do any work during that time, would he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.13,0:11:14.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm afraid so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,0:11:17.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I’m having these thoughts every now and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.60,0:11:20.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that the Lord\Nleft our family to our own devices?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.79,0:11:23.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Clara, stop saying nonsense like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:27.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.67,0:11:29.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sleeping soundly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.22,0:11:31.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He looked exhausted, so I let him sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:36.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Them, I'll bring him his meal\Nwhen he wakes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:37.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now, everyone, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.00,0:11:40.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:58.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Dear Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:16.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.86,0:12:22.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'm not taking you to school ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:26.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Little?\NAre you disobeying what I tell you to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:27.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You can't come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:31.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You understand, don’t you, Little?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:37.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:41.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Lucy rejected you\Nand took flight, didn’t she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.89,0:12:43.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little, I'm going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.09,0:12:59.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll put here what we should line up next.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:00.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'll do it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:02.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I can do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:06.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How is your father doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.19,0:13:10.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,His body feels so heavy he can barely move,\Nso he just complains all day long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.70,0:13:12.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He still can't use his leg, can he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:14.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, he became very irritable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.26,0:13:17.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, oh my, our Mr. Popple?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.64,0:13:19.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dad is an unlucky man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.08,0:13:21.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You can’t know that for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.29,0:13:25.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Still, that’s what I feel keenly\Nwhenever I see him these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.29,0:13:29.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Despite all his effort up to now,\Nhe couldn’t get any land.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.00,0:13:31.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There’s no good job for him either,\Non top of that, he got injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:35.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You should take bad things off your mind.\NI’m sure, it’ll turn to better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.20,0:13:40.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I’m trying to think that before long,\Ngood things will start happening to us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:43.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, welcome!
Comment: 0,0:13:44.50,0:13:46.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.78,0:13:47.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:49.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.77,0:13:56.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy-May is made to stand again!\NLucy-May is made to stand again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.41,0:13:59.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy-May is made to stand again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.87,0:14:00.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I’ll get you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.40,0:14:01.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! She spilled some!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:06.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We’ll tell everything to teacher!\NWe’ll tell everything to teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.80,0:14:08.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We’ll tell...
Comment: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:09.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:14:09.97,0:14:11.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.79,0:14:20.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, I won’t be talking during the class anymore,\Nso please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:35.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher! Teacher!\NMy head is starting to hurt already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.55,0:14:37.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Try to forgive me, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.00,0:14:49.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that’s better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.89,0:14:54.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:11.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, good, good.
Comment: 0,0:15:12.19,0:15:14.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:18.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This despicable guy is coming.\NI don’t wanna meet him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.81,0:16:02.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.47,0:16:06.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A bird's nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:10.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what kind of bird\Nbuilt its nest at a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.79,0:16:19.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Must be a bird that likes collecting strange things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.32,0:16:22.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A button, eyeglasses, a crooked nail.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:24.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:28.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It’s money.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.43,0:16:52.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.63,0:16:56.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little, hear this! I found some money!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:03.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So, what will you do with that money?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:05.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Gonna buy something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:06.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:07.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Something!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:11.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You know, on the town square on Carrington Street,\Nthey hold auctions all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.93,0:17:15.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I think we can buy something wonderful there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.42,0:17:16.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Not with just five shillings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:18.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Five is more than none at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.21,0:17:21.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure this money is something\Nthe Lord bestowed upon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:24.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It’s just some money that fell on the pavement\Nthat the bird picked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.80,0:17:28.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The bird carried it to its own nest,\Nwhere you snatched it, didn’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:30.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.12,0:17:33.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You’re going shopping with me or not? Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:35.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:38.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I'll go with you\Nonce I’m done with this work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:42.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you won’t be able to buy much\Nwith just five shillings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:45.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t need much,\Njust one wonderful thing would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:49.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,After all, it’s the first time\NI made some money myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:51.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What was that? Didn’t you just pick it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.02,0:17:53.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You can’t use the word “made”\Nfor something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.69,0:17:55.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But that’s how the grown-ups use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.18,0:17:59.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, it’s not the word\Nthe children would use.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:00.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.98,0:18:02.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, how about a cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:03.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.78,0:18:07.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In the bakery where Clara works,\Nthey have very delicious cakes, don’t you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:09.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Five shillings should be enough to buy a cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:10.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.61,0:18:15.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But a cake would be gone\Nafter we’ve eaten it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.52,0:18:17.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:19.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This feels like a bit of a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:20.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.71,0:18:22.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It’s fine. A cake is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.40,0:18:26.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to know what it’s like\Nto get full on cakes at least once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.23,0:18:28.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You can’t buy that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.24,0:18:28.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:29.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:32.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Say, isn’t that Clara over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.85,0:18:33.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.89,0:18:39.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange. She’s supposed\Nto still be in the shop at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.19,0:18:41.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like she's pondering on something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.65,0:18:43.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My, she didn’t even notice us just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:48.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? She’s heading in the direction\Nopposite to the bakery.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:48.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna call her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:51.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a moment. Let's see where she's going\Nby following her first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:53.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We’ll follow her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:55.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do just that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.62,0:19:06.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My heart is racing, sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.68,0:19:21.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,She entered this store.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.29,0:19:23.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of store is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.38,0:19:25.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like a fabric store, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:27.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It’s where they sell fabric for sewing clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.51,0:19:30.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This store seems awfully expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:34.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.60,0:19:35.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:37.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna come inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:40.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Clara would notice us at once if we do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.80,0:19:42.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Isn’t it all the same if she does?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.88,0:19:44.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.90,0:19:50.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It could only be that Clara came here\Nto buy some fancy fabric for clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.19,0:19:51.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.82,0:19:52.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.73,0:19:53.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's you two again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.78,0:19:55.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.79,0:19:57.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing at a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.11,0:20:01.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What are {\i1}you{\i0} doing at a place like this, sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.20,0:20:05.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What I’m doing is of none concern to you,\Ndon’t you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.98,0:20:09.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But we thought you’d be at work\Nin the bakery right about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:11.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.12,0:20:14.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But there was something I needed to deliver\Nto this part of the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.75,0:20:16.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And on my way back, I made a bit of a detour...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.78,0:20:19.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But why did you stop by this fabric store?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.18,0:20:20.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s call that my secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:26.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You know, we saw you there on the main street\Nand followed you all the way to here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.13,0:20:31.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But it seems you’ve been so preoccupied\Nwith your own thoughts, you never noticed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.72,0:20:32.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So you followed me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.59,0:20:37.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. But we couldn’t help\Nfinding it bizarre somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.79,0:20:40.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see. You sensed it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.60,0:20:49.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You two, if you promise not to spill it to anyone else,\NI might tell you what my secret is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.73,0:20:51.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.76,0:20:53.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I promise too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.69,0:20:56.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, come inside then, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:04.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Miller?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:07.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, did you forget something?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:08.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.91,0:21:11.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to distract you,\Nknowing how busy you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.61,0:21:14.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But could you please show my order\Nto my sisters as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.70,0:21:19.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.29,0:21:23.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What did you mean by “your order”?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.44,0:21:24.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Fabric, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.93,0:21:27.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Did you buy it in order to make a dress?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.90,0:21:30.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, more or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.21,0:21:31.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I’m wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.49,0:21:33.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If you put it that way...\NLet’s keep it this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.17,0:21:43.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That’s a truly wonderful quality item you bought.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:45.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I believe, your little sisters would be proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.56,0:22:01.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It’s the very best item we have in this shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.88,0:22:05.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Such a beautiful fabric!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.34,0:22:08.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Could we possibly feel it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.20,0:22:11.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If you’ve clean hands, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.77,0:22:18.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! It’s so smooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.52,0:22:20.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,True!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.60,0:22:23.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It’s for a weddings dress, isn’t it, Clara?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.24,0:22:27.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It’s bound to make for a supreme wedding dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.49,0:22:30.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you were the one who bought this fabric, Clara?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.87,0:22:34.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Month after month, Ms. Popple\Nkeeps paying for it, little by little,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.79,0:22:37.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,until it finally becomes her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.38,0:22:38.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.93,0:22:40.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Clara, you're incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.20,0:22:43.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, don't rejoice just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.70,0:22:47.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We can’t exactly say it fully belongs to me yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.60,0:22:49.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.14,0:22:52.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In truth, I still owe a bit more for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.14,0:22:55.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it’ll be fully yours\Nas soon as next month, Ms. Popple.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.49,0:22:58.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you’ve only five shillings more to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.41,0:23:00.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Five shillings?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.15,0:23:05.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I’m just five shillings away\Nfrom really owning this beautiful fabric, at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.20,0:23:09.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sister, you can already consider this fabric yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.41,0:23:14.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Just let me pay those final five shillings for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.40,0:23:16.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.42,0:23:23.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy's money was used to pay for the fabric\Nthat was to become Clara’s wedding dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.89,0:23:45.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I still wonder, what kind of bird it was,\Nthe one that picked up those five shillings?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.46,0:24:06.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,While returning from the port,\Nwe were assaulted by a gang!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.22,0:24:10.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Among the passengers riding that carriage with us,\Nwas Mr. Pettywell, carried with him a sum of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.89,0:24:14.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Lucy-May of the Southern Rainbow:\N"Robbers on the Prairie".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.77,0:24:16.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
